<script>
	option = {
	    color: ['#3398DB'],
	    tooltip: {
	        trigger: 'axis',
	        axisPointer: {            // 坐标轴指示器，坐标轴触发有效
	            type: 'shadow'        // 默认为直线，可选为：'line' | 'shadow'
	        }
	    },
	    grid: {
	        left: '3%',
	        right: '4%',
	        bottom: '3%',
	        containLabel: true
	    },
	    xAxis: [
	        {
	            type: 'category',
	            data: ['Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat', 'Sun'],
	            axisTick: {
	                alignWithLabel: true
	            }
	        }
	    ],
	    yAxis: [
	        {
	            type: 'value'
	        }
	    ],
	    series: [
	        {
	            name: '直接访问',
	            type: 'bar',
	            barWidth: '60%',
	            data: [10, 52, 200, 334, 390, 330, 220]
	        }
	    ]
	};
</script>
